title: Stanley Turrentine - 1992 - More Than A Mood FLAC
description:
Stanley Turrentine - 1992 - More Than A Mood

For this quartet date with pianist Cedar Walton, bassist Ron Carter and drummer Billy Higgins (trumpeter Freddie Hubbard sits in on two numbers), Turrentine is in top form on a variety of standards plus Tommy Turrentine's "Thomasville" and Rahsaan Roland Kirk's "Spirits up Above." A fine session. (AllMusic)

Track list:
01 - Thomasville
02 - They Can't Take That Away From Me
03 - In a Sentimental Mood
04 - Easy Walker
05 - Triste
06 - Pieces of Dreams
07 - Spirit Up Above
08 - More Than a Mood
